---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Our Services – Guzman Tax Accounting Las Vegas" description="Professional tax, bookkeeping, payroll, LLC and more. Bilingual staff in Las Vegas, Nevada." lang="en" langHref="/servicios">
<section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/en/">Home</a> <span>›</span> <span>Services</span></div><h1>Our Services</h1><p>Bilingual Accounting Firm in Las Vegas — complete solutions for individuals and businesses.</p></div></section>
<section class="section"><div class="container">
  <div class="services-grid" style="margin-bottom:60px;">
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 3H7a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v16a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h10a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V9z"/><path d="M14 3v6h6"/></svg></div><h3>Tax Preparation</h3><p>Personal and business taxes: 1040, LLC, S-Corp, C-Corp. We maximize your refund legally.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="4" y1="20" x2="20" y2="20"/><line x1="7" y1="20" x2="7" y2="14"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="9"/><line x1="17" y1="20" x2="17" y2="4"/></svg></div><h3>Bookkeeping</h3><p>Monthly reconciliation, accounting records and clear financial statements for your business.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="3.5"/><path d="M4 20c0-4.4 3.6-8 8-8s8 3.6 8 8"/></svg></div><h3>Payroll Services</h3><p>Payroll processing, W-2, 1099, direct deposit and federal/state tax compliance.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L20.5 7v10L12 22 3.5 17V7z"/></svg></div><h3>LLC Formation</h3><p>We help you form your LLC correctly, including EIN, operating agreement and state compliance.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="13" rx="1"/><path d="M3 7l9 7 9-7"/></svg></div><h3>IRS Letters & Audits</h3><p>Response and representation for IRS letters, audits and tax compliance support.</p></div>
    <div class="service-card"><div class="service-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="14" rx="1"/><line x1="2" y1="8" x2="22" y2="8"/></svg></div><h3>Web Design & E-Commerce</h3><p>Free 1-page website when you create an LLC or hire our professional services. Hosting included.</p></div>
  </div>
  <div class="cta-section" style="border-radius:16px;"><h2>Have Questions?</h2><p>Schedule a free consultation and we will explain everything with no commitment.</p><div class="btn-group"><a href="/en/free-consultation" class="btn btn-primary">Free Consultation</a><a href="tel:+17253406758" class="btn btn-white">Call Now</a></div></div>
</div></section>
</Layout>
